    Paramount Pictures Corp.
    Sony Pictures Entertainment Inc.
    Universal Pictures/MCA.
    Telecommunications Inc.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>AUZ  Australia.
    USZ  United States of America.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
