FT  22 NOV 94 / UK Company News: Charles Baynes makes acquisitions for
Pounds 7.2m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Charles Baynes, the engineer, is spending Pounds 7.2m, in cash, to expand
its aerospace components and valves activities.
Its Kent Aerospace Castings subsidiary has bought the business and assets of
